  "prompt": "Which are the most romantic songs in Malayalam?",
  "response": "Malayalam cinema has produced a plethora of romantic songs over the years, cherished by many for their poignant lyrics and melodious tunes. Here are some of the most romantic songs in Malayalam:\n\n1. **\"Kannum Kannum Thamilarasi\"** from \"Angadi\" (1980) - Sung by K.J. Yesudas and P. Susheela, this timeless classic evokes deep emotions.\n2. **\"Oru Mukham Mathram\"** from \"Poothaakoru Mookuthi\" (1988) - A beautifully sung duet by K.J. Yesudas and K.S. Chithra.\n3. **\"Ariyathe Ariyathe\"** from \"Bangalore Days\" (2014) - A modern romantic song sung by Vijay Yesudas and Mehnaz.\n4. **\"Mazhaye Thoomazhaye\"** from \"Pattam Pole\" (2013) - Sung by Haricharan, it captures the essence of love during the rain.\n5. **\"Melle Melle\"** from \"Thirakkatha\" (2008) - Sung by K.S. Chithra, a melodious number expressing the gentleness of love.\n6. **\"Kannu Thurannu\"** from \"Chengazhi Nambiar\" (2002) - A heartfelt romantic melody sung by K.J. Yesudas.\n7. **\"Manassinte Ullil\"** from \"Anweshichu Kandethiyilla\" (1967) - A golden oldie sung by K.J. Yesudas.\n8. **\"Pavizhamazhaye\"** from \"Athiran\" (2019) - Sung by K.S. Harisankar, it's a song that beautifully describes the feeling of being in love.\n\nThese songs span different eras of Malayalam cinema, showcasing the rich musical legacy that has contributed to the romance genre.",
